name:           rewire-core
version:        2.7
synopsis:       A Haskell-to-Verilog/VHDL compiler, core library (Hyle to RTL plus shared base)
description:    The ReWire core. The Hyle bit-level IR, its checker/optimizer/interpreter/parser, the Verilog/VHDL/Cryptol RTL backends, and the shared base utilities (annotations, diagnostics, config, pretty-printing). Consumed by rewire-frontend.
category:       Language
homepage:       https://github.com/rewire-hardware/ReWire#readme
bug-reports:    https://github.com/rewire-hardware/ReWire/issues
author:         Adam Procter,
                Chris Hathhorn <hathhorn@gmail.com>,
